{
  "texts": [
    "Evaluation MetricsThe evaluation of the integrated model's performance and its reduction in hallucination was based on a set of carefully selected metrics.",
    "Those metrics were chosen to ensure a comprehensive assessment of the model, covering both its linguistic capabilities and its ability to integrate real-time information accurately.",
    "The following list details each metric and provides justification for its inclusion:• BLEU (Bilingual Evaluation Understudy): Measures the linguistic quality of the generated text by comparing it with reference texts.",
    "This metric is crucial for evaluating the fluency and grammatical coherence of the model's output, ensuring that the integration does not compromise the textual quality.-Necessity: BLEU is widely used in NLP for assessing translation quality, making it a reliable benchmark for linguistic accuracy in generated text.• ROUGE (Recall-Oriented Understudy for Gisting Evaluation): Assesses content similarity between the generated text and reference texts, focusing on the recall of critical information.-Necessity: ROUGE is essential for evaluating how well the model captures the key points from the input or background information, reflecting its comprehension and content generation capabilities.• Custom Hallucination Metric: Compares the factual accuracy of the model's output against verified data sources.",
    "This metric involves manual verification of a random sample of generated texts to identify instances of hallucination, complemented by automated checks against trusted databases.-Necessity: Given the specific aim to reduce hallucination, this custom metric directly addresses the model's ability to generate factually accurate and trustworthy content, crucial for applications requiring high reliability.• Response Time: Measures the time taken for the model to generate a response, evaluating the impact of the Google Query API integration on the speed of text generation.-Necessity: Maintaining efficient response times is vital to ensure the usability of the model in realtime applications, making this metric important for assessing the practicality of the integration.• Relevance of Queried Information: Assesses the utility of the information retrieved through the Google Query API in enhancing the generated text's accuracy and relevance."
  ]
}